data.description: This gorgeous residence offers both luxury and comfort including 5 spacious bedrooms, 4 full bathrooms, beautiful open floor plan with the primary suite conveniently located on the main level. This inviting home features high ceilings throughout the entrance and dining room area, as well as a beautiful staircase leading you to the second level. A very spacious chef's kitchen with stainless steel appliances, double door pantry, plentiful cabinetry, double wall ovens, and a beautiful countertop base with granite finishes. Upstairs you'll find the media room with ample space to host various gatherings. Enjoy the peacefulness and views of nature overlooking the greenbelt on the covered patio or the second-floor deck. Feel secure in this quite and calm neighborhood with controlled access, as well as enjoy the community pool, playground, and park for outdoor recreation.
